headline: Goldman Sachs Raises its Price Target on Targa Resources Corp. (TRGP) to $242 and Maintains a Buy Rating
summary: Targa Resources Corp. (NYSE:TRGP) is among the 10 High Growth S&P 500 Stocks to Buy Now. Goldman Sachs, on February 20, 2026, raised its price target on Targa Resources Corp.
